definitions.definition: A powered heavier-than-air aircraft with fixed wings .
A game to encourage small children to eat, in which the parent or carer pretends a spoonful of food is an aircraft flying into the child's mouth.

main_definition: ( chiefly US , Canada , Philippines ) A powered heavier-than-air aircraft with fixed wings .
